       contain a valid encoding for a rrssaa_lleenn byte RSA key in the
       respective encoding method and stores the recovered data
       of at most ttlleenn bytes (for RRSSAA_NNOO_PPAADDDDIINNGG: of size ttlleenn)
       at ttoo.

       For RSA_padding_xxx_OAEP(), pp points to the encoding
       parameter of length ppll. pp may be NNUULLLL if ppll is 0.

